    dc:title "Olopachys (Olopachylaella) gronychi subgen. nov., sp. nov., a new species of mite from Bulgaria (Acari: Mesostigmata: Pachylaelapidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177209>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177208>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177211>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177210> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177209>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 9. Olopachys gronychi sp. nov. 3. Male, chelicera, lateral view; 4. Female, sperm access system; 5. Female, chelicera, lateral view; 6. Male, palptibial outgrowths, palp cross-section; 7. Male, leg II, lateral view, with ventral detail of femoral apophysis; 8. Female, epistome; 9. Female, tarsus II, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177209/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177208>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Olopachys gronychi sp. nov. Female. 1. Dorsal idiosoma; 2. ventral idiosoma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177208/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177211>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 24. Olopachys spp., Female, sperm access system. 16. O. crassipes; 17. O. annae; 18. O. kacheticus; 19. O. caucasicus; 20. O. compositus; 21. O. adsharicus; 22. O. golubevi; 23. O. suecicus; 24. O. sklari. Figures not to scale. Figs 16 – 22 and 24 modified from Koroleva (1977)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177211/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.177210>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 15. Olopachys (Olopachys) spp., general appearance. 10. Male, palptibial outgrowths, palp cross-sections; 11. Female, sperm access system of O. vysotskajae; 12. Female, chelicerae, lateral views; 13. Male, leg II, lateral view; 14. Male, chelicerae, lateral views; 15. Female, epistome. Figures not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177210/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

